description: Ask alexa for a joke. All jokes are based on US states.  For example say "Alexa, ask state jokes for a joke".  Alexa responds with a random joke for example: "In what state do you get sick and bother people? Illinois."
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask state jokes for a joke
Alexa, ask state jokes to tell me a joke
Alexa, ask state jokes to give me a state joke
name: State Jokes
shortDescription: Ask alexa for a joke. All jokes are based on US states.  For example: "In what state do you get sick and bother people? Illinois."
